-- ============================================================================
-- Ragebot Aimbot v3.1 (UNDETEK-style keyboard UI)
-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- This version replaces the click-driven GUI with a keyboard-navigated menu
-- inspired by UNDETEK:
--
--   * ENTER     : toggle the aimbot on/off (master switch)
--   * UP / DOWN : move the selection cursor through menu items
--   * LEFT/RIGHT: change the selected item's value
--                 - toggles:  LEFT=OFF, RIGHT=ON
--                 - sliders:  LEFT=decrease, RIGHT=increase
--                 - dropdowns: LEFT=prev option, RIGHT=next option
--   * INSERT    : show/hide the GUI
--   * R         : reset smooth-aim progress
--
-- If the user tries to click a menu item with the mouse, the aimbot
--   1) yanks the cursor to a random screen edge via mousemoverel
--   2) shows a legacy-style Roblox message box:
--      "use your keyboard, not mouse thx"
--
-- The menu frame itself is still draggable by the title bar (so you can
-- reposition the panel without triggering the troll).
--
-- All bug fixes from v3.0 are preserved.
-- ============================================================================

if not game:IsLoaded() then
    game.Loaded:Wait()
end

